==German==
===Etymology===
Compound of ''[[ab]]'' and ''[[biegen]]''
===Transitive Verb===
'''abbiegen'''

# to [[bend]]
# (''tech'') to [[fold]] (metal)
# ''fig.'' to [[head off]], to [[stave off]]

===Intransitive Verb===
'''abbiegen'''

# to [[turn]], to [[turn off]]
# to [[branch off]]

